#. module: partner_credit_checks
#: model:res.partner.dossier,description:partner_credit_checks.dossier_reliable
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Clients with good payment history and documentation in order, but with certain exposure limits. \n"
"        Require periodic reviews and standard guarantees. \n"
"        Ideal for recurring clients with moderate operations.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Clientes con buen historial de pagos y documentación en regla, pero con ciertos límites de exposición. \n"
"        Requieren revisiones periódicas y garantías estándar. \n"
"        Ideales para clientes recurrentes con operaciones moderadas.\n"
"        "

#. module: partner_credit_checks
#: model:res.partner.dossier,description:partner_credit_checks.dossier_highly_reliable
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Clients with impeccable credit history, updated documents and no incidents. \n"
"        Access to the highest credit limits and preferential conditions. \n"
"        Require minimal collateral and are usually strategic or long-standing partners.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Clientes con historial crediticio impecable, documentos actualizados y sin incidencias. \n"
"        Acceso a los límites de crédito más altos y condiciones preferenciales. \n"
"        Requieren garantías mínimas y suelen ser socios estratégicos o de larga trayectoria.\n"
"        "

#. module: partner_credit_checks
#: model:res.partner.dossier,description:partner_credit_checks.dossier_low_reliability
msgid ""
"\n"
"        New customers, with limited history or previous incidences (delinquency, overdue documents). \n"
"        Restricted credits or advance payments. \n"
"        Require additional guarantees and frequent validations to mitigate risks.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Clientes nuevos, con historial limitado o incidencias previas (morosidad, documentos vencidos). \n"
"        Créditos restringidos o pagos por adelantado. \n"
"        Requieren garantías adicionales y validaciones frecuentes para mitigar riesgos.\n"
"        "

